Descrição: ND-5 is a modified BX Commando droid, originally built by the Separatists during the Clone Wars. ND-5 was deployed to a dozen frontlines across the galaxy before being placed in deep storage at the end of the war. In the age of the Empire, the deadly droid has been working with Jaylen Vrax. ND-5 now operates as Vrax’s personal enforcer and has been assigned to join Kay Vess’ crew for a very important heist.
